{"tid":1681293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記唔記得點解話遊行唔好去港島？","createTime":"2019-10-29T10:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:00:34.000Z","uid":41355,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"59f453592e1dacd8643c96115345b1dbdc51262c","tid":1681293,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">難出難入 難帶gear</span></strong><br />\n地鐵唔計<br />\n基本上三條過海隧道set road block就check晒<br />\n加埋巴士班次疏<br />\n出入都唔方便<br />\n有gear更加危險<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">地形難打</span></strong><br />\n得三條主要道路<br />\n夏愨道、電車路同皇后大道<br />\n狗隻淨係需要針對呢三街路佈防，好易針對，be water唔到<br />\n唔似旺角咁向內街一閃就得<br />\n加埋灣仔有幾條天橋<br />\n好易截龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好出港島<br />\n文宣做左咁耐，出就梗<br />\n但係我地要諗下<strong>令遊行順利d</strong><br />\n如果狗隻開戰，我地要<strong>點樣應對</strong>"},{"pid":"804d85dae8005034176783f981c46d352e47051b","tid":1681293,"uid":41355,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"首先要準時同人多<br />\n只要人多逼爆晒cwb令狗隻無訂企<br />\n再蔓延出去<br />\n勇武就可以順利入場"},{"pid":"71bd8bcc0b1a4689dcf76b8847d30a0309dfad1f","tid":1681293,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd170024e584c33ca483f254537a8d7bd0cc507e","tid":1681293,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:26:55.000Z","msg":"好快就11.2架啦"},{"pid":"939599ad249100579a574616688f1e2e57ef607c","tid":1681293,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de2687376b4da7b8616b5dd1e032744626bf7cc8","tid":1681293